/**
 * Feature: Page Cache
 *
 * TODO: Implement full page caching system
 *
 * MISSING CAPABILITIES (vs WP Rocket/NitroPack):
 * - Full page HTML caching
 * - Device-specific caching (mobile/desktop/tablet)
 * - User-specific caching (logged in/out)
 * - Cache preloading/warmup
 * - Automatic cache invalidation
 * - Cache purging by URL, category, tag
 * - Browser caching headers
 * - GZIP compression
 * - Separate cache for different query strings
 * - Cache exclusion rules (URLs, cookies, user agents)
 *
 * IMPLEMENTATION NOTES:
 * - Store cached files in wp-content/cache/wps-page-cache/
 * - Use advanced-cache.php dropin for early caching
 * - Implement cache key based on: URL, device type, user status, query vars
 * - Add HTML comment with cache info (timestamp, cache hit)
 * - Support cache lifespan configuration
 * - Implement garbage collection for old cache files
 *
 * INTEGRATION POINTS:
 * - Hook into 'save_post' for automatic invalidation
 * - Hook into 'comment_post' for comment pages
 * - Hook into 'switch_theme' to purge all cache
 * - Add WP-CLI commands for cache management
 * - Add admin bar menu for cache purging
 *
 * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
 * - Serve cache before WordPress loads (advanced-cache.php)
 * - Use file system cache (faster than database)
 * - Implement efficient cache key hashing
 * - Add cache statistics dashboard
 * - Monitor cache hit/miss ratio
 *
 * COMPATIBILITY:
 * - Detect and warn about conflicting cache plugins
 * - Support WooCommerce (don't cache cart/checkout)
 * - Support membership plugins (user-specific caching)
 * - Support WPML/Polylang (language-specific caching)
 *
 * @package WPS\CoreSupport
 * @since 1.2601.75000
 */

